@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor #FAFAFA
skinparam classBackgroundColor #FFF3E0
skinparam classBorderColor #E65100
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
[*] --> Created
Created --> Delivered : cancel
Created : entry / log route
Delivered --> Reviewed : submit
Reviewed --> OnHold : confirm
OnHold --> Closed : review
OnHold --> Delivered : revert
Closed --> [*]
@enduml